Barry Quin https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Barry_Quin 0 Barry Quin (born 1949) is a British-Australian who is a stage and television actor, best known for his role in the original cast of Prisoner playing Dr. Greg Miller. He was married to his Prisoner co-star Peta Toppano during the early 1980s, but they divorced after ten years; he has since remarried.
